title: United Kingdom 1 Month Bill Yield
description: UK 1 Month Bond Yield was 2.35 percent on Thursday November 3, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the United Kingdom 1 Month Bill Yield reached an all time high of 12.50 in September of 1992. This page includes a chart with historical data for UK 1M.
